Celebrated stylish pastor and motivational speaker Robert Burale is happy to be alive. The fashion critic suffered a minor head injury and was admitted at the Nairobi Hospital. Burale had posted something on social media hinting that the devil had knocked his door but through God, he was able to overpower him (the devil). He said, “When the devil thought he had me down... God got my back and I walked out of STRONGER.” It’s not clear whether Burale fell or something hit him, but thank God he is out of danger. After he was attended to by a doctor, the father of one shared another post, which read, “I walked out stronger. Who said God is not my healer? THE BLOOD SPEAKETH…”